title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Fantasy 5' game
maintext:
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Fantasy 5” game were:
05-28-29-38-40
(five, twenty-eight, twenty-nine, thirty-eight, forty)
Estimated jackpot: $915,000
